 Requirements
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - MVC Framework v1.0.0 or later 
 - ApPHP Directy CMF v2.7.0 or later 

 Modules Installation/Update:
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - https://www.apphp.com/php-directy-cmf/index.php?page=module-installation-and-update
 
 Usage:
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
 In HTML template:
 
	<?php
		if($this->isHomePage){
			echo BannersComponent::drawSlider(array(
				'width' 		=> '1170',
				'height' 		=> '400',
				'navigation' 	=> 'true',
				'delay'			=> 5000
			));
		}						
	?>					
 
 In CMS pages:
 
	{module:banners}

